               <interp inst="t17951202-28-person365" type="given" value="Q."></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17951202-28-person365" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                  </persName>
            Which hand did you take hold of him with? - A. My left.</p>
               <p>Q. Your left side must be turned towards him? - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Are you not blind on that side? - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Then you venture to say, from that instantaneons view, that you had such an oppertunity of observing him, as to swear he is the same man you saw in the court? - A. He did not come out first.</p>
               <p>Q. Did they not come out together? - 
               <persName id="t17951202-28-person366">
                  A. 
               <interp inst="t17951202-28-person366" type="given" value="A."></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17951202-28-person366" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                  </persName>
            They came out near together.</p>
