               <interp inst="t17951202-28-person368" type="given" value="Q."></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17951202-28-person368" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                  </persName>
            Was any thing found upon him that was lost from Mr. Mangnell's? - A. No.</p>
               <p>Mr. Gurney. - 
               <persName id="t17951202-28-person369">
