               <interp inst="t17951202-28-person369" type="given" value="Q."></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17951202-28-person369" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                  </persName>
            You never saw Smith till you saw him at the watch-house? - A. I saw him coming out at the gates.</p>
