                     <interp inst="t17951202-28-person373" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                  </persName>
            If you cast them all three, you know, you will get an hundred and twenty pounds; do not you expect a share of that? - A. I do not know; if there is a share, I suppose it will be given to me; if they are cast for death I shall expect something of course.</p>
               <p>Mr. Shepherd. - Q. Did you see the watchmen when they were in the court? - A. I saw them as they entered the court just before me, and I followed behind.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17951202-28-person374">
